other_tests.procedure_name: CT abdomen and pelvis with contrast
other_tests.findings: Appendix is dilated and thickened measuring up to 9 mm in diameter. Minimal periappendiceal inflammatory changes noted. No fluid collection/abscess surrounding the appendix. The remainder of the bowel is unremarkable in appearance. Uterus and ovaries are visualized; follicular changes noted within both ovaries.
